Thorns

One of the most basic druidic spells, this charm allows
the druid to strike a target with a barrage of sharp
thorns.  Though its damage is limited, especially against
armored targets, its low cost and rapid recovery time
mean that even some heirophant druids consider it a
useful part of their arsenal.

Command: thorns <target> (defaults to attacker)
Base Cost: 25 SP
Base Recovery: fast
Base Effect: damage (low)
Base Duration: instant
Guild Level: 1
